{{About|[[Audio player (software)|audio player]] software|hardware devices|Comparison of portable media players}}

The following '''comparison of audio players''' compares general and technical information for a number of software [[media player (application software)|media player]] programs. For the purpose of this comparison, "audio players" are defined as any media player explicitly designed to play audio files, with limited or no support for video playback. Multi-media players designed for video playback, which can also play music, are included under [[comparison of video player software]].

