==Optical media ability==
Information about what kinds of [[optical disc]]s the players can play. Footnotes lead to information about abilities of future versions of the players or plugins that provide such functionality.
Playback of [[Super Audio CD]] is not possible for any media player, because no suitable hardware exists.
All media players capable of [[Compact Disc|audio CD]] playback will also play the [[Red Book (audio CD standard)|Redbook]] core of any [[High Definition Compatible Digital|HDCD]] disc, providing no sound-quality benefits over standard audio CDs.

